{"tid":2275064,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"【移民加拿大】為加快經濟復甦　加拿大計劃未來3年吸納120萬名移民","createTime":"2020-11-07T01:31:30.000Z","updateTime":"2020-11-07T04:58:42.000Z","uid":141151,"like":14,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":27,"replies":[{"pid":"329df63801f55b676604cd907390952316348880","tid":2275064,"uid":141151,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-07T01:31:30.000Z","msg":"【移民加拿大】為加快經濟復甦　加拿大計劃未來3年吸納120萬名移民<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://wealth.hket.com/article/2793200/%E3%80%90%E7%A7%BB%E6%B0%91%E5%8A%A0%E6%8B%BF%E5%A4%A7%E3%80%91%E7%82%BA%E5%8A%A0%E5%BF%AB%E7%B6%93%E6%BF%9F%E5%BE%A9%E7%94%A6%E3%80%80%E5%8A%A0%E6%8B%BF%E5%A4%A7%E8%A8%88%E5%8A%83%E6%9C%AA%E4%BE%863%E5%B9%B4%E5%90%B8%E7%B4%8D120%E8%90%AC%E5%90%8D%E7%A7%BB%E6%B0%91\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwealth.hket.com%2Farticle%2F2793200%2F%25E3%2580%2590%25E7%25A7%25BB%25E6%25B0%2591%25E5%258A%25A0%25E6%258B%25BF%25E5%25A4%25A7%25E3%2580%2591%25E7%2582%25BA%25E5%258A%25A0%25E5%25BF%25AB%25E7%25B6%2593%25E6%25BF%259F%25E5%25BE%25A9%25E7%2594%25A6%25E3%2580%2580%25E5%258A%25A0%25E6%258B%25BF%25E5%25A4%25A7%25E8%25A8%2588%25E5%258A%2583%25E6%259C%25AA%25E4%25BE%25863%25E5%25B9%25B4%25E5%2590%25B8%25E7%25B4%258D120%25E8%2590%25AC%25E5%2590%258D%25E7%25A7%25BB%25E6%25B0%2591&d=J7URIij%2BjV7QbFiEH5rjuItKjO%2FIGoH7AJS0Ocrd4mI%3D&h=21b1a3b6\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://wealth.hket.com/article/2793200/%E3%80%90%E7%A7%BB%E6%B0%91%E5%8A%A0%E6%8B%BF%E5%A4%A7%E3%80%91%E7%82%BA%E5%8A%A0%E5%BF%AB%E7%B6%93%E6%BF%9F%E5%BE%A9%E7%94%A6%E3%80%80%E5%8A%A0%E6%8B%BF%E5%A4%A7%E8%A8%88%E5%8A%83%E6%9C%AA%E4%BE%863%E5%B9%B4%E5%90%B8%E7%B4%8D120%E8%90%AC%E5%90%8D%E7%A7%BB%E6%B0%91</a><br />\n<br />\n新冠肺炎疫情大流行下，令不少人的移民計劃被逼暫時擱置。向來是移民國家的加拿大，為了彌補疫情期間移民人數減少，以及加快疫情後的經濟復甦，計劃於未來3年內接收120萬名移民，明年新增永久居民人數的目標為約40萬人。<br />\n<br />\n<strong>明年目標吸納約40萬新永久居民<br />\n</strong><br />\n加拿大移民部長Marco Mendicino於上周五發布會時透露，加拿大將計劃於未來3年內接收120萬名移民，明年新增永久居民人數的目標為約40萬人，2022年目標人數為41.1萬人，2023年則為42.1萬人。<br />\n<br />\nMendicino指，移民是加拿大短期經濟復甦及長期繁榮的關鍵，政府將致力於吸納海外勞工，以填補國內勞動力短缺的缺口。 <br />\n<br />\n加拿大商會勞工部門高級總監Leah Nord表示，即使加拿大失業率處於歷史高點，但部份行業或地區仍有職位空缺，移民將繼續在填補勞動力短缺方面發揮重要作用。"},{"pid":"4b8a14c82ce2e754c0cca093d48e00ac860919f3","tid":2275064,"uid":115510,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-07T01:33:41.000Z","msg":"Nice<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"974045cb7127b2c31f7afda80319d80222307ea1","tid":2275064,"uid":221650,"like":2,"dislike":1,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-07T01:34:46.000Z","msg":"加拿大係會不斷擴大移民計劃，增加移民名額，降低移民資格"},{"pid":"a0f533ac60310321fa1ffbd23a79fa6b8da90544","tid":2275064,"uid":256837,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-07T01:37:12.000Z","msg":"左膠總理又多120萬票<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b38df5b400139bf3a6e666931e1832dcb61fde83","tid":2275064,"uid":34410,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-07T01:38:42.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />加拿大想引入120萬支那有錢佬？"},{"pid":"94ed5ebffef8cd2d06a45b80379f2ce78372ecff","tid":2275064,"uid":28845,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":6,"replyTime":"2020-11-07T01:52:16.000Z","msg":"高失業率但又職位空缺<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"89ef11fe512d64e3b6e9c1ab34b1444286025074","tid":2275064,"uid":198856,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"94ed5ebffef8cd2d06a45b80379f2ce78372ecff","tid":2275064,"uid":28845,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":6,"replyTime":"2020-11-07T01:52:16.000Z","msg":"高失業率但又職位空缺<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-11-07T01:54:17.000Z","msg":"咪係，想點<img src=\"/assets/faces/cat/sneeze.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"cdc8d2e7f58b5be30221544d26c3620483d4312f","tid":2275064,"uid":36995,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"